body:
## What's Changed

* Added: Swift 5.6 support (https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/5).
* Infrastructure: CI optimizations (https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/1; https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/4).

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/compare/0.1.0...0.1.1

## What's Changed

* Fixed: Don't merge escaped dependencies with current task local value (thanks @tgrapperon, https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/11).
* Infrastructure: Documentation and README fixes and updates (thanks @tgrapperon, in https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/6; https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/8; https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/9).

## New Contributors

* @tgrapperon made their first contribution in https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/6

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/compare/0.1.1...0.1.2

## What's Changed
* Fixed: Don't setup observers in non-test contexts https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/14

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/compare/0.1.2...0.1.3

## What's Changed

* Fixed: Dependency values returning optionals no longer return `nil` instead of their default values (thanks @pyrtsa, https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/29).
* Fixed: If `liveValue` and `previewValue` are defined, a default `testValue` implementation will now properly invoke the `previewValue` and not the `liveValue` (https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/30).
* Infrastructure: Updated README with quick start usage (https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/24) and documentation updates (thanks @oronbz, https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/26, https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/27, https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/28).

## New Contributors

* @oronbz made their first contribution in https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/27
* @pyrtsa made their first contribution in https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/pull/29

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-dependencies/compare/0.1.3...0.2.0
